# Cloud File Picker Configuration (all optional)
#
# If these are not set, the corresponding picker buttons will show as "Not configured"
# and agents using onedrive-file / google-drive-file UiSchema types will gracefully degrade.

# OneDrive / SharePoint — Azure AD app registration
# Required: Register an app at https://portal.azure.com → App registrations
# Redirect URI (SPA): {your-origin}  (e.g. http://localhost:5173 for local dev)
# API permissions: Files.Read (delegated, user-consentable)
# Auth flow: MSAL.js Auth Code + PKCE (no redirect HTML file needed)
VITE_ONEDRIVE_CLIENT_ID=

# Google Drive — Google Cloud Console OAuth + Picker API
# Required: Enable "Google Picker API" at https://console.cloud.google.com
# Create OAuth 2.0 Client ID (Web application), set authorized JS origins to your domain
# Scopes: https://www.googleapis.com/auth/drive.readonly
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=
